        "id": 10009
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-12-15T20:50:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Eric, Kevin: Thank you both for your input. Using the \"prod\" tag for now SGTM, but in the long term we\u0027ll want an autoroller to peg the Skia WASM container to a specific ta, which makes the build reproducible. Let\u0027s discuss the appropriate roll frequency after we\u0027ve migrated at least one of the Skia WASM apps to Bazel.",
      "parentUuid": "49d892cf_63f0a2b2",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 3104,
        "startChar": 30,
        "endLine": 3105,
        "endChar": 52
      },
      "revId": "874d6539860ba34ca19be6c10b925162701d721b",
