      "message": "\u003e I would still like a comment at the top of index.bzl pointing to WORKSPACE since it\u0027s not otherwise obvious of that connection.\n\nI disagree, at some point we have to assume some basic knowledge of Bazel.",
      "parentUuid": "e4ea2675_e3af5b22",
